  "heading_path": "气体动理论 / 压强和温度的微观解释",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 93,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02808:aeed4d09991d]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02809:84b1c046d96c]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02810:e6a155fd9544]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02811:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02812:83a7a2035c51]]显然温度一样，而He单个分子质量更小，所以压强更大。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02813:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02814:97c9fd5f3fd6]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02815:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02816:4024f862fe9e]] \n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02817:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02818:ff5997c5ef48]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02819:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02820:379a015adb51]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02821:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02822:a16d680f6eed]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02823:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02824:3e898a3d94b0]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02825:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02826:a48d24f48f08]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02827:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02828:0b703e9cd2f8]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02829:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02830:daddbfef9af0]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02831:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02832:5d206348e48a]]\n 所以压强，温度都变为原来的 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02833:1dadbbd6331b]] 倍。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02834:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02835:58155778529c]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02836:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02837:081288edf7e1]] \n其中 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02838:f91d3c8a48b2]] 是分子数密度。分子有效直径 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02839:d41e87806cca]] 在这个模型中也不随温度改变，当 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02840:6db4b82fbf48]] 由 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02841:1a1a435825a8]] 升到 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02842:63c9d9ee6cad]] 时，[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02843:aa0690b134ca]]， [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02844:90a193bdaf0b]]。其余不变。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02845:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02846:037930b99a0c]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02847:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02848:e7fd91255ced]] 表示速率在 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02849:3a951bdaab2a]] 区间内的分子数占总分子数的百分率。\n对速率大于 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02850:664eef176723]] 的分子，平均速率为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02851:bf12a21a8a9e]] \n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02852:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02853:44aa6bd4fcf6]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02854:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02855:f67e9be2871c]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02856:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n",
  "mode": "REWRITE",
